What the fuck have you done?

01:05:51.430 --> 01:05:54.090
一片混乱
It's a goddamn mess. I'll tell you that.

01:05:59.630 --> 01:06:03.370
-这些是什么？  -你说呢  全是寄给你的
-What's all this?  -You tell me, fuck-stick. They're all addressed to you.

01:06:04.640 --> 01:06:05.970
看下这个
Take it.

01:06:14.520 --> 01:06:16.010
“杜弗伦先生：”
"Dear Mr. Dufresne,

01:06:17.150 --> 01:06:19.120
“鉴于你再三询问，”
In response to your repeated enquiries,

01:06:19.320 --> 01:06:23.590
“本州特拨款给贵图书馆。”
the State has allocated the enclosed funds for your library project."

01:06:24.360 --> 01:06:26.190
有两百元
This is $200.

01:06:26.390 --> 01:06:30.090
“另外，主管单位”
"In addition, the Library District has generously responded...

01:06:30.100 --> 01:06:33.160
“特地捐赠旧书及杂物，”
with a charitable donation of used books and sundries.

01:06:33.370 --> 01:06:37.500
“相信可满足阁下需要，就此了结，”
We trust this will fill your needs. We now consider the matter closed.

01:06:37.710 --> 01:06:39.500
“勿再来信。”
Please stop sending us letters."

01:06:39.740 --> 01:06:42.400
典狱长回来前清理干净
I want all this cleared out before the Warden gets back.

01:06:42.640 --> 01:06:43.800
是
Yes, sir.

01:06:48.080 --> 01:06:49.240
干得好  安迪
Good for you, Andy.

01:06:52.220 --> 01:06:53.350
哇！
Wow!

01:06:54.560 --> 01:06:56.490
只写了六年
It only took six years.

01:06:58.060 --> 01:07:00.790
现在起我一周两封
From now on, I'll write two letters a week, instead of one.

01:07:01.000 --> 01:07:04.330
你真够固执的  听队长的话
Oh, I believe you're crazy enough. You'd better get all this stuff out,

01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:07.030
把东西清干净  我去解大便
like the Captain said. Now, I'm gonna go pinch a loaf.

01:07:07.240 --> 01:07:08.730
别让我出来
When I come back,

01:07:08.900 --> 01:07:10.670
再看到这些
this is all gone, right?

01:07:37.910 --> 01:07:38.980
如何修理任一汽车的任一部分

01:07:37.910 --> 01:07:38.980
加戈头漫画

01:07:59.020 --> 01:08:00.820
安迪  什么声音？
Andy, do you hear that?

01:09:09.560 --> 01:09:10.720
杜弗伦
Dufresne?

01:09:13.260 --> 01:09:14.790
安迪  放我出去！
Andy, let me out!

01:09:17.770 --> 01:09:19.130
安迪！
Andy?

01:09:21.670 --> 01:09:26.610
到现在我还搞不懂她们唱什么
I have no idea to this day what those two Italian ladies were singing about.

01:09:21.670 --> 01:09:31.840
这首曲子出自莫扎特的歌剧《费加罗的婚礼》第三幕，
女主角苏珊娜（Susanna）与伯爵夫人（la Contessa）的二重唱
《待到微风轻轻吹过（Che Soave Zeffiretto）》（又称《微风拂面》）；
剧中三等家仆费加罗要和女仆苏珊娜结婚，受到怀有不轨之心的伯爵重重阻挠，
于是两位女士设计写一封信，邀花心的伯爵傍晚到树林幽会，使其落入陷阱出丑；
歌词很短，很简单，几乎就是伯爵夫人念一句，苏珊娜复述一次，然后写在信上：
伯爵夫人：希望能够吹起柔柔的西风……  苏珊娜：西风……
伯爵夫人：今晚会有风吧……  苏珊娜：今晚……
伯爵夫人：在林中松树的下面……  苏珊娜：松树的下面……
伯爵夫人：这样写，下面应该就知道了吧！  苏珊娜：应该会知道吧！
伯爵夫人：微风轻吹的歌啊！

01:09:26.910 --> 01:09:29.140
其实我也不想弄懂
The truth is, I don't want to know.

01:09:29.340 --> 01:09:31.840
此时无言胜有言
Some things are best left unsaid.

01:09:35.420 --> 01:09:38.150
她们唱出
I like to think they were singing about something so beautiful,

01:09:35.420 --> 01:09:43.590
这部歌剧为什么对肖申克众囚犯有那么大的触动呢？
在当时的奥地利，仆人没有任何地位，
按当时的规矩，仆人结婚，新娘的初夜权是主人的，
社会上废除农奴制的呼声，开始出现；
这部歌剧的作曲水平很高，情感通过音乐完美传达给观众，
因此，公演后在维也纳激起强烈反响，民众同情费加罗的遭遇，更加支持废除农奴制，
很快，全欧掀起革命，莫扎特的理想实现了——他通过他的作品，为社会进步贡献了力量。
“即使我的舌头尝到了死亡的味道，我的音乐依然是乐观的。”——莫扎特

01:09:38.350 --> 01:09:40.480
难以言传的美
it can't be expressed in words...

01:09:40.690 --> 01:09:43.590
美得令你心碎
and makes your heart ache because of it.

01:09:45.260 --> 01:09:47.750
歌声直窜云端
I tell you, those voices soared...

01:09:48.030 --> 01:09:52.330
超越失意囚徒的梦想
higher and farther than anybody in a gray place dares to dream.

01:09:52.530 --> 01:09:55.900
宛如小鸟飞入牢房
It was like some beautiful bird flapped into our drab little cage...

01:09:56.100 --> 01:09:58.870
使石墙消失无踪
and made those walls dissolve away.

01:09:59.310 --> 01:10:01.500
就在这一瞬间
And for the briefest of moments...

01:10:01.710 --> 01:10:04.700
肖申克众囚仿佛重获自由
every last man at Shawshank felt free.

01:10:07.280 --> 01:10:09.940
典狱长可发飚了
It pissed the Warden off something awful.

01:10:11.250 --> 01:10:12.240
开门
Open the door.

01:10:15.160 --> 01:10:16.920
开门
Open it up!

01:10:18.230 --> 01:10:20.960
杜弗伦  开门
Dufresne, open this door!

01:10:22.300 --> 01:10:23.490
关掉
Turn that off!

01:10:30.570 --> 01:10:33.010
我警告你  关掉
I am warning you, Dufresne. Turn that off!

01:10:47.120 --> 01:10:49.090
杜弗伦
Dufresne!

01:10:50.760 --> 01:10:52.280
敬酒不吃吃罚酒
You're mine now.

01:10:59.730 --> 01:11:02.970
安迪被关禁闭两周
Andy got two weeks in the hole for that little stunt.

01:11:03.170 --> 01:11:04.760
站起来
On your feet.

01:11:05.940 --> 01:11:08.340
-看谁来了  -大指挥家
-Hey, look who's here.  -Maestro!

01:11:05.940 --> 01:11:08.340
大师（ Maestro）是意大利语，通常为技艺高超的音乐家的统称，
但时常也可用以称呼其他艺术门类里的艺术家，
可以指称：乐器演奏家、作曲家、指挥家以及教师。

01:11:10.110 --> 01:11:13.770
你没别的可放吗？  比如汉克·威廉斯的歌？
Y-Y-You couldn't play something good, huh? Hank Williams or something?

01:11:10.110 --> 01:11:13.770
汉克·威廉斯（Hank Williams），一生仅仅活了29年的美国乡村音乐歌手，
他的歌曲中，除了浓厚的乡村风味，很多带有蓝调的成份，
有歌迷将他比做文学界的莎士比亚，因为不知怎么那么悲伤和凄凉，
但其实他的妻子对他无微不至，即使他们后来离婚，她都爱他到最终；
他是西部歌曲之王，美国乡村西部歌曲存在这么多年，还没有一个歌手可以说自己超越汉克·威廉斯。

01:11:14.120 --> 01:11:16.910
没等接受点歌  他们就破门而入了
They broke the door down before I could take requests.

01:11:17.120 --> 01:11:20.250
-关两周值得吗？  -我最舒服的两周
-Was it worth it, two weeks in the hole?  -Easiest time I ever did.

01:11:20.460 --> 01:11:24.650
-屁话  小号最难熬了  -在里面度日如年
-Bullshit! There's no such thing as easy time in the hole. -A week in the hole is like a year.

01:11:24.860 --> 01:11:28.160
-半点不假  -有莫扎特陪我
-Damn straight.  -I had Mr. Mozart to keep me company.

01:11:28.360 --> 01:11:31.330
他们准你带留声机？
So, they let you tote that record player down there, huh?

01:11:33.770 --> 01:11:35.130
在脑中
It was in here.

01:11:35.970 --> 01:11:37.200
在心底
And in here.

01:11:38.340 --> 01:11:40.430
音乐之美
That's the beauty of music.

01:11:40.640 --> 01:11:42.970
是夺不走的
They can't get that from you.

01:11:46.510 --> 01:11:48.880
你没体会过吗？
Haven't you ever felt that way about music?

01:11:50.690 --> 01:11:53.810
我年轻时吹过口琴
Well, I played a mean harmonica, as a younger man.

01:11:54.860 --> 01:11:56.550
后来没兴致了
Lost interest in it, though.

01:11:56.760 --> 01:11:58.350
在牢里也没意义
Didn't make much sense in here.

01:11:58.690 --> 01:12:00.680
就是在这里才有意义
Here's where it makes the most sense.

01:12:01.230 --> 01:12:03.290
有音乐才不会忘记
You need it, so you don't forget.

01:12:03.870 --> 01:12:05.060
忘记什么？
Forget?

01:12:05.430 --> 01:12:08.530
世上
Forget that...

01:12:08.740 --> 01:12:10.170
有些地方
there are places...

01:12:10.670 --> 01:12:14.510
是石墙围不住的
in the world that aren't made out of stone.

01:12:15.510 --> 01:12:17.000
在人的
There's something...

01:12:17.350 --> 01:12:18.740
内心深处
inside...

01:12:19.010 --> 01:12:20.980
有他们找不到
that they can't get to...

01:12:21.180 --> 01:12:22.550
拿不走的东西
that they can't touch.

01:12:23.080 --> 01:12:24.520
完全属于你自己的东西
It's yours.

01:12:26.050 --> 01:12:27.650
你指什么？
What are you talking about?

01:12:28.690 --> 01:12:29.920
希望
Hope.

01:12:30.990 --> 01:12:32.320
希望
Hope?

01:12:34.260 --> 01:12:36.250
朋友  我告诉你
Let me tell you something, my friend.

01:12:37.070 --> 01:12:39.360
有希望才危险
Hope is a dangerous thing.

01:12:40.540 --> 01:12:42.870
希望能把人逼疯
Hope can drive a man insane.

01:12:43.600 --> 01:12:45.730
在这里  希望毫无用处
It's got no use on the inside.

01:12:45.940 --> 01:12:48.140
你最好认命
You'd better get used to that idea.

01:12:50.650 --> 01:12:52.140
要像老布一样吗？
Like Brooks did?

01:13:17.510 --> 01:13:18.490
坐下
Sit down.

01:13:23.850 --> 01:13:27.140
根据你的材料 你的终身监禁已经服满30年
It says here that you've served 30 years of a life sentence.

01:13:28.320 --> 01:13:30.380
你改过自新了吗？
You feel you've been rehabilitated?

01:13:30.590 --> 01:13:31.810
是的
Oh, yes, sir.

01:13:33.090 --> 01:13:34.420
我真的已经变好了
Without a doubt.

01:13:35.590 --> 01:13:37.990
我完全洗心革面了
I can honestly say I'm a changed man.

01:13:39.990 --> 01:13:41.930
我不会再危害社会
No danger to society here.

01:13:42.460 --> 01:13:43.990
我向上帝发誓
God's honest truth.

01:13:46.570 --> 01:13:48.660
我绝对改过自新了
Absolutely rehabilitated.

01:13:52.390 --> 01:13:54.200
驳    回

01:13:58.710 --> 01:14:00.040
30年了
Thirty years.

01:14:02.020 --> 01:14:03.920
老天  真不知该说什么？
Jesus, when they say it like that...

01:14:04.790 --> 01:14:06.580
这些日子怎么熬过来的
You wonder where it went.

01:14:09.020 --> 01:14:11.180
我连前十年都不记得了
I wonder where 10 years went.

01:14:16.160 --> 01:14:17.190
拿去
Here.

01:14:17.630 --> 01:14:20.360
假释被拒的礼物
A little parole rejection present.

01:14:21.640 --> 01:14:23.330
打开看看
Go ahead and open it.

01:14:24.440 --> 01:14:26.460
别介意我找你同行买
I had to go through one of your competitors.

01:14:26.670 --> 01:14:29.800
我只想给你一个惊喜
I hope you don't mind. I wanted it to be a surprise.

01:14:39.850 --> 01:14:41.340
漂亮极了
It's very pretty, Andy.

01:14:43.060 --> 01:14:44.250
谢谢
Thank you.

01:14:46.830 --> 01:14:48.320
你不吹吗？
Are you going to play it?

01:14:52.870 --> 01:14:54.130
不
No.

01:14:57.740 --> 01:14:59.140
不是时候
Not right now.

01:15:16.820 --> 01:15:17.920
进牢
Roll in!

01:15:31.090 --> 01:15:36.160
瑞德 赠

01:15:31.090 --> 01:15:36.160
十周年庆

01:15:54.130 --> 01:15:55.360
熄灯
Lights out!

01:16:29.960 --> 01:16:32.090
安迪言出必行
Andy was as good as his word.

01:16:32.470 --> 01:16:35.230
每周写两封信
He wrote two letters a week instead of one.

01:16:37.310 --> 01:16:41.400
59年  州议会终于明白
In 1959, the State Senate finally clued into the fact...

01:16:41.640 --> 01:16:44.770
两百元无法打发安迪
they couldn't buy him off with just a $200 check.

01:16:44.980 --> 01:16:49.280
当局决定每年拨款五百美元
Appropriations Committee voted an annual payment of $500...

01:16:49.480 --> 01:16:51.380
好让安迪封笔
just to shut him up.

01:16:51.590 --> 01:16:54.580
你想像不到他的能耐
And you'd be amazed how far Andy could stretch it.

01:16:54.790 --> 01:16:57.720
他接洽读书会  慈善团体
He made deals with book clubs, charity groups.

01:16:57.930 --> 01:17:00.690
他论斤买入旧书
He bought remaindered books by the pound...

01:17:01.200 --> 01:17:02.720
《金银岛》
"Treasure Island".

01:17:03.260 --> 01:17:04.600
罗伯特·路易斯
Robert Louis...

01:17:04.800 --> 01:17:05.820
史蒂文森
Stevenson.

01:17:06.030 --> 01:17:07.400
冒险小说类
Fiction, adventure.

01:17:09.970 --> 01:17:10.990
下一本
What's next?

01:17:11.210 --> 01:17:14.270
汽车维修
I got here Auto Repair...

01:17:15.010 --> 01:17:16.170
肥皂雕刻
and Soap Carving.

01:17:16.380 --> 01:17:19.610
专业技术及嗜好  教育类  在你后面
Trade skills and hobbies. Goes under "Educational". The stack behind you.

01:17:19.810 --> 01:17:21.680
基堵山恩仇记
The Count Of Monte Crisco.

01:17:22.150 --> 01:17:24.450
基督山  饭桶
That's "Cristo", you dumb shit.

01:17:25.550 --> 01:17:26.540
作者亚历山大……
By Alexandree...

01:17:27.020 --> 01:17:28.280
大种马
Dum-ass.

01:17:28.620 --> 01:17:29.650
种马？
Dumb ass.

01:17:31.960 --> 01:17:33.020
种马？
Dumb ass?

01:17:35.930 --> 01:17:37.900
大仲马  内容知道吗？
Dumas. You know what that's about?

01:17:40.170 --> 01:17:42.140
讲逃狱  你会喜欢的
You'd like it. It's about a prison break.

01:17:42.340 --> 01:17:46.240
那该归入教育类啰
We ought to file that under "Educational", too, oughtn't we?

01:17:47.110 --> 01:17:51.200
大伙儿尽可能地帮忙
The rest of us did our best to pitch in when and where we could.

01:17:51.780 --> 01:17:53.540
在肯尼迪遇刺那年
By the year Kennedy was shot,

01:17:53.480 --> 01:17:56.600
布鲁克斯·海特伦图书纪念馆

01:17:53.780 --> 01:17:58.280
安迪把这间臭储藏室变成
Andy had transformed a storage room smelling of rat turds and turpentine...

01:17:58.590 --> 01:18:01.680
新英格兰最棒的监狱图书馆
into the best prison library in New England,

01:18:02.390 --> 01:18:05.330
甚至有汉克·威廉斯精选集
complete with a fine selection of Hank Williams.

01:18:12.700 --> 01:18:14.630
就在同年
That was also the year Warden Norton...

01:18:14.840 --> 01:18:17.770
典狱长实施著名的“外役”专案
instituted his famous "Inside Out" program.

01:18:18.240 --> 01:18:20.300
也许你曾在报上看过
You may remember reading about it.

01:18:20.540 --> 01:18:23.640
他上了各报和《展望杂志》
It made all the papers and got his picture in Look Magazine.

01:18:23.840 --> 01:18:25.140
这不是放任自由
It's no free ride...

01:18:25.350 --> 01:18:28.580
而是狱政的
but rather a genuine, progressive advance...

01:18:28.780 --> 01:18:31.270
一大进步
in corrections and rehabilitation.

01:18:31.620 --> 01:18:34.140
本监服刑人在妥善监督下
Our inmates, properly supervised,

01:18:34.360 --> 01:18:36.980
将到狱外劳动
will be put to work outside these walls,

01:18:37.190 --> 01:18:40.290
从事各项公共事业
performing all manner of public service.

01:18:40.460 --> 01:18:43.260
他们将学到诚实劳动的价值
These men can learn the value...

01:18:43.460 --> 01:18:47.260
同时为社区提供服务
of an honest day's labor, while providing a valuable service to the community...

01:18:47.470 --> 01:18:52.170
对于纳税大众而言  也只花最少的代价
and at a bare minimum of expense to Mr. and Mrs. John Q Taxpayer.

01:18:52.610 --> 01:18:54.940
当然  诺顿没向媒体说明
Of course, Norton failed to mention to the press...

01:18:55.140 --> 01:18:58.600
“最少代价”实在含糊不清
that "bare minimum of expense" is a fairly loose term.

01:18:58.810 --> 01:19:01.840
揩油的方法何止百种
There are 100 different ways to skim off the top.

01:19:02.050 --> 01:19:04.540
人力  物料  处处漏洞
Men, materials, you name it.

01:19:04.890 --> 01:19:07.790
天哪  油水超多
And, oh, my Lord, how the money rolled in.

01:19:07.990 --> 01:19:10.510
-这样下去  你会害我倒闭的  -内德
-If this keeps up, you'll put me out of business. -Ned!

01:19:10.720 --> 01:19:15.200
-靠这么多奴工  谁投标投得过你  -内德
-This pool of slave labor you've got, you can underbid any contractor in town. -Ned,

01:19:15.730 --> 01:19:18.700
我们在提供社区服务
we're providing a valuable community service here.

01:19:18.900 --> 01:19:23.300
这是说词  我得养家
Well, that's fine for the papers, but I've got a family to feed.

01:19:25.240 --> 01:19:26.760
山姆  咱们这么久的交情
Sam, we go back a long way.

01:19:28.080 --> 01:19:33.010
我需要包下这条公路  不然只好喝西北风了
I need this new highway contract. I don't get it, and I go under. That's a fact.

01:19:33.910 --> 01:19:35.710
这是我太太特地为你烤的派
You just have some of this fine pie...

01:19:35.950 --> 01:19:39.280
请笑纳
my missus made especially for you, and you think about that.

01:19:47.560 --> 01:19:50.260
别担心这项工程合约
Ned, I wouldn't worry too much about this contract.

01:19:50.500 --> 01:19:53.560
我已叫他们接别的项目了
