So I'm backing out the door, right? And I got the TV like this.

01:24:40.420 --> 01:24:44.050
它很大  害我看不见  忽然传来
It was a big old thing. I couldn't see shit. Suddenly, I hear this voice.

01:24:44.690 --> 01:24:46.660
