Well, I just stand there, holding onto that TV. So, finally, the voice says,

01:24:51.530 --> 01:24:55.330
他又说  “你听到没有？”  我说  “听到，但我若松手，”
"Do you hear what I said, boy?" I say, "Yes, sir. I sure did.

01:24:55.540 --> 01:24:58.990
