Promise me, Red.

01:46:50.750 --> 01:46:52.380
如果你终获假释
If you ever get out,

01:46:52.590 --> 01:46:54.080
去找到那个地方
find that spot.

01:46:55.250 --> 01:47:00.090
石墙底下有一块奇石
At the base of that wall, you'll find a rock that has no earthly business in a Maine hayfield.

01:47:01.230 --> 01:47:04.250
黑色火山玻璃石
A piece of black, volcanic glass.

01:47:06.930 --> 01:47:09.590
底下埋着给你的东西
There's something buried under it I want you to have.

01:47:10.370 --> 01:47:11.600
是什么？
What, Andy?

01:47:12.040 --> 01:47:13.770
你埋着什么？
What's buried under there?

01:47:15.370 --> 01:47:17.240
你搬开它
You'll have to pry it up...

01:47:17.440 --> 01:47:18.710
