Oh, Lord.

01:47:40.970 --> 01:47:42.560
怎么了？
What?

01:47:43.300 --> 01:47:46.070
安迪今天到载货区
Andy come down to the loading dock today.

01:47:46.270 --> 01:47:48.370
问我要一条绳子
He asked me for a length of rope.

01:47:48.570 --> 01:47:51.270
-绳子？  -六英尺长
-Rope? -Six feet long.

01:47:51.510 --> 01:47:52.880
你给了他？
And you gave it to him?

01:47:53.750 --> 01:47:55.540
为什么不给？
Sure I did. Why wouldn't I?

01:47:55.750 --> 01:47:59.680
-天啊  赫伍  -我怎么想得到？
-Jesus, Heywood. -Hey, how the hell was I supposed to know?

01:48:00.090 --> 01:48:01.640
你忘了老布？
Remember Brooks Hatlen?

01:48:01.820 --> 01:48:05.590
不  安迪不会寻短
No. Andy would never do that.

01:48:06.190 --> 01:48:07.250
绝对不会
Never.

01:48:09.330 --> 01:48:10.660
谁知道呢？
I don't know.

01:48:13.500 --> 01:48:15.520
人的忍耐是有限度的
Every man has his breaking point.

01:48:17.870 --> 01:48:20.130
动作快  我要回家
Lickety-split. I want to get home.

01:48:20.440 --> 01:48:22.200
马上好了
Just about finished, sir.

01:48:39.330 --> 01:48:40.950
今晚要存三笔
Three deposits tonight.

01:48:48.930 --> 01:48:50.830
把衣物送洗
Get my stuff down to the laundry.

01:48:51.040 --> 01:48:52.660
把鞋擦亮
And shine my shoes.

01:48:52.870 --> 01:48:55.810
-要擦得雪亮  -是
-I want 'em looking like mirrors. -Yes, sir.

01:49:01.310 --> 01:49:02.800
你回来真好  安迪
It's good having you back, Andy.

01:49:03.720 --> 01:49:05.580
没有你可差多了
The place wasn't the same without you.

01:49:52.460 --> 01:49:53.520
熄灯
Lights out!

01:50:26.370 --> 01:50:28.890
我也曾熬过孤寂长夜
I've had some long nights in stir.

01:50:29.440 --> 01:50:32.100
独自在心中思东想西
Alone in the dark with nothing but your thoughts,

01:50:32.300 --> 01:50:34.970
