Let's go, let's go! Move your butts! Move it!

01:53:08.130 --> 01:53:09.120
站好
Stand.

01:53:10.560 --> 01:53:11.620
你说
Well?

01:53:15.070 --> 01:53:16.060
说什么？
Well, what?

01:53:16.270 --> 01:53:19.730
你们俩成天粘在一起
I see you two all the time. You're thick as thieves, you are.

01:53:20.810 --> 01:53:22.300
他一定说过什么
He must have said something.

01:53:23.040 --> 01:53:24.570
报告典狱长
No, sir, Warden.

01:53:24.910 --> 01:53:25.900
没有
Not a word.

01:53:27.750 --> 01:53:30.310
那真是奇迹了
Lord, it's a miracle!

01:53:30.920 --> 01:53:33.480
人像屁一样凭空消失
A man up and vanished like a fart in the wind.

01:53:34.150 --> 01:53:35.310
不见踪影
Nothing left...

01:53:36.150 --> 01:53:38.880
只剩一堆石头
but some damn rocks on a windowsill.

01:53:39.090 --> 01:53:41.820
还有墙上那骚货  问问她吧
And that cupcake on the wall. Let's ask her.

01:53:42.030 --> 01:53:43.790
也许她知道些什么
Maybe she knows.

01:53:43.830 --> 01:53:46.760
你来说  短裤妞儿
What say there, Fuzzy Britches? Feel like talking?

01:53:47.200 --> 01:53:49.500
她不会说的
Ah... I guess not.

01:53:50.070 --> 01:53:52.260
别人不说  为何她要说
Why should she be any different?

01:53:53.340 --> 01:53:55.000
没错  你们有预谋
This is a conspiracy.

01:53:55.640 --> 01:53:57.470
就是这样
That's what this is.

01:53:58.080 --> 01:54:01.810
