In 1966,

01:54:42.820 --> 01:54:45.220
安迪·杜弗伦逃离……
Andy Dufresne escaped...

01:54:45.420 --> 01:54:46.980
肖申克监狱
from Shawshank Prison.

01:54:49.230 --> 01:54:51.790
狱方只寻获泥渍囚衣
All they found of him was a muddy set of prison clothes,

01:54:52.430 --> 01:54:53.960
一块肥皂
a bar of soap...

01:54:54.170 --> 01:54:55.720
和一把石锤
and an old rock hammer...

01:54:55.930 --> 01:54:58.430
一把几乎解体的石锤
damn near worn down to the nub.

01:55:02.910 --> 01:55:07.680
我曾夸口要花六百年才能挖通的隧道
I remember thinking it would take a man 600 years to tunnel through the wall with it.

01:55:08.310 --> 01:55:10.940
安迪花了不到20年
Old Andy did it in less than 20.

01:55:29.230 --> 01:55:31.530
他喜爱研究地质
Oh, Andy loved geology.

01:55:32.300 --> 01:55:35.470
碎石令他想一探究竟
I imagine it appealed to his meticulous nature.

01:55:35.870 --> 01:55:37.710
